    "name": "ESPIONAGE: Mafia Evolved",
    "steam_appid": 1174380,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1174380/extras/d16ee17eab1b879953b0fd1adcc561eb.avif?t=1742080395\" width=600 height=223 /></span><br>In 1958, on an island beyond the North Sea, a tournament of deduction is hosted by the last of a once-defunct criminal enterprise. Invited are an assortment of personalities that find there are few strangers amongst them, but all are promised a solitary reward for the eventual winner: &quot;No wish will go ungranted&quot;. However, the specialized device each player now wears is used not only to participate in the game but compel them toward revelations none expect.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Play Solo vs. AI or up to 8 players with any combination of humans and AI<br></li><li>Full cross-play between PC, Android and IOS<br></li><li>Full cross-progression<br></li><li>No pay-to-win mechanics<br></li><li>No ads and no limits on play<br></li><li>Anonymous mode<br></li><li>Achievements<br></li><li>Multiple languages supported<br></li><li>Frequent updates</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Gameplay:</h2><br><strong><i>TEAM SPY</i></strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Frame the Detective for arrest or Eliminate them and ensure the Spy escapes.</li></ul><br><strong><i>TEAM DETECTIVE</i></strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Arrest the Spy before they escape.</li></ul><br><strong><i>Use your AP carefully</i></strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Action Points (AP) allow you to perform actions with and against other players. Make allies and enemies as you navigate the match and help your side win—all while being undermined by your opponents. </li></ul><br><strong><i>Find as much Intel as you can</i></strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Reaching 100% Trust with another player will allow the two of you to exchange Intel.<br></li><li>Every list of Intel contains the names of two players who are NOT the Detective or Informant—use this to find your allies, and your opponents, before it's too late.</li></ul><br><strong><i>Be wary of Suspicion</i></strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>You and other players will be raising one another's Suspicion toward the other throughout the game—and those with enough Suspicion are nominated for arrest. When it's time for voting, only they are in danger of leaving the match... </li></ul>",
